cast.overview: When a band of brutal gangsters led by a crooked property developer make a play to take over the city, Master Ip is forced to take a stand.
cast.title: Ip Man 3

details.biography:
Karena Ng (born Wu Qian Yu, 吳千語) is an actress and model from Hong Kong.

She started off in 2010 in an advertisement for Tempo tissue paper, and started her acting career in 2011 in the Hong Kong comedy Magic to Win directed by Wilson Yip. She was nominated for the Best New Performer award in the 31st Hong Kong Film Awards. More recently, she acted in Ip Man 3 as a single teacher Miss Wong.

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
